{"tid":1989872,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共黨員指舉報不上組織，黨民無視法律照賣敏感題材。","createTime":"2020-04-26T10:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T10:04:16.000Z","uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb853c1648b213bec0f47bdf36f8fc765008b87","tid":1989872,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"內容大意：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">steam上有自稱中共黨員指，台灣人的舉報是上不到中央的，中共国內目前豬肉緊張，禁止遊戲即是&quot;說一套做一套&quot;平民和黨員依舊視法律如無物。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自稱是中共黨員，在深圳工作站偵查體溫工作，很有錢，可以參軍打台灣並捐100萬買火箭炮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtiLE9g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtiLE9g.png&h=b840c15a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/appu6Mk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fappu6Mk.png&h=ef8b7b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聲稱自己黨員，說話代表黨，指遊戲被禁止，但還有在賣。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZmpVEH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZmpVEH.png&h=81205adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指中国国內存在豬肉問題。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44eCwc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44eCwc3.png&h=d8fbe338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指中国檢舉網是中国90後控制，情報不會上報中央。<br />\n笑指台灣人動作多餘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm9V2jK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm9V2jK.png&h=9193f34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指香港警察不如公安，學歷低，看到洋人就軟了。<br />\n並質疑特首為何不對歐美封關。(當中還將不封關的原由推給醫護)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5VRAK3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5VRAK3.png&h=17a076db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suZZKx5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuZZKx5.png&h=b5a71281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再次指出，有法律我們黨也不會理，平民繼續賣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRZrpx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRZrpx6.png&h=940d374a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GXTOZN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GXTOZN.png&h=3698b4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsG1XS8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsG1XS8.png&h=4256c7db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指台灣己在中国監視下，隨時可以留島不留人，並笑台灣只能買美國殘次品。<br />\n(PO主指你們都把槍對準台灣，為何要跟敵國買武器？)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fn8S4Fi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFn8S4Fi.png&h=9500ceef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對方未公開個人資料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/urvKbkv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FurvKbkv.png&h=c34241bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友比啲NMLS人勁啲，講野都有根據，話吹哨34人都被追封，又捉晒啲紅會同官員喎。<br />\n跟手一堆NMLS人一直NMLSNMLS無野睇。"}]}